org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class UnknownRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.RecordBase
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.Record
        • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.StandardRecord
          • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.UnknownRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class UnknownRecord
extends StandardRecord
    Unknown record just tells you the sid so you can figure out what records you are missing. Also helps us read/modify sheets we don't know all the records to. (HSSF leaves these alone!)(未知记录只是告诉您sid，以便您可以弄清楚您丢失了哪些记录。还可以帮助我们阅读/修改我们不知道的所有记录的工作表。(HSSF别管这些！）)

    • Field Detail

      • PRINTSIZE_0033

        public static final int PRINTSIZE_0033
        seems to be part of the PageSettingsBlock. Not interpreted by POI. The name 'PRINTSIZE' was taken from OOO source.

        The few POI test samples with this record have data { 0x03, 0x00 }.

        (似乎是PageSettingsBlock的一部分。未由兴趣点解释。“PRINTSIA”这个名字取自OOO来源。具有此记录的少数DOE测试样本具有数据{0x 03，0x 00}。)

      • UnknownRecord

        public UnknownRecord(RecordInputStream in)
        construct an unknown record. No fields are interpreted and the record will be serialized in its original form more or less(构建未知记录。没有字段被解释，记录将或多或少以其原始形式序列化)
        Parameters:
        in - the RecordInputstream to read the record from(in -用于读取记录的RecordInputstream)
